HEADWORD: De rigueur
<hw>De ri`gueur"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[F. See 2d
<er>Rigor</er>.]</ety> <def>According to strictness (of etiquette, rule,
or the like); obligatory; strictly required.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

